# Wordpress Toolbox

## Description

Command line tools for managing a wordpress website.

## Installation

```pip install wordpress_toolbox```

or

```pipenv install wordpress_toolbox```

## Usage

```wpt get-post https://www.hostname.com 9999```

```wpt get-posts https://www.hostname.com```

